                        <div class="panel" data-content="content-1">
                            <p>É uma técnica totalmente manual que não precisa utilizar aparelhos, usamos óleo de coco para deslizamento. Mas podemos usar qualquer produto.</p>
                        </div>

                        <button class="accordion" data-to-content="content-2"><span>Conteúdo programático</span><svg version="1.1" id="Capa_1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 451.846 451.847" style="enable-background:new 0 0 451.846 451.847;" xml:space="preserve"><g><path d="M345.441,248.292L151.154,442.573c-12.359,12.365-32.397,12.365-44.75,0c-12.354-12.354-12.354-32.391,0-44.744 L278.318,225.92L106.409,54.017c-12.354-12.359-12.354-32.394,0-44.748c12.354-12.359,32.391-12.359,44.75,0l194.287,194.284 c6.177,6.18,9.262,14.271,9.262,22.366C354.708,234.018,351.617,242.115,345.441,248.292z"/></g><g></g><g></g><g></g><g></g><g></g><g></g><g></g><g></g><g></g><g></g><g></g><g></g><g></g><g></g><g></g></svg></button>
